  m_text: 'Honor Among Thieves is a 2-player co-op game where players work together
    to escape a maze before the time runs out.


    Red and Blue have pulled off
    their grandest heist yet: stealing computer data! Selling these on the black
    market should net them a couple thousand bucks. However, the computer''s security
    protocols have been triggered, trapping them in a maze. Play as Red and Blue
    as you work together to escape the maze before you get caught!'
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
